  "texts": [
    "Each 90-min focus group was facilitated by a professional American moderator with expertise in both facilitation and LLMs.",
    "For the purpose of the pilot, this dual expertise was important in ensuring that the moderator could craft the moderation guides alongside the authors and navigate any unanticipated questions or challenges.",
    "In the focus group, the moderator would explain LLM chatbots, outline the participants' rights and expectations, and answer any questions the participants raised prior to or during the deliberations.",
    "During deliberation, the moderator guided participants to elucidate their views on the appropriateness of the chatbot responses, provide some reasoning for their initial answer to the survey, and share any further thoughts in light of what other participants had said.",
    "They also ensured that the participants stayed on topic, took turns speaking, and kept time."
  ],
